# 31 : LABYRINTH-OF-APOCKALYPSE — game-design atop Substrate
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# § I> "Apockalypse" is the canonical project-spelling (creator-canonical
#       per Apocky-direction + apocky13 attestation). ¬ "Apocalypse".
#       N! "correct" to Apocalypse anywhere in this doc-tree.
# § I> LoA = Labyrinth-of-Apockalypse. composes §§ 30_SUBSTRATE primitives
#       into the game. content-side of the bootstrap arc.
# § I> stage-0 design ; DESIGN-ONLY @ S8-H0. impl @ phase-I (session-9+).
# § I> existing project-vector :
#       - Labyrinth-of-Apocalypse (legacy Rust @ ~/source/repos)
#       - Infinite-Labyrinth lineage (C# IL + multiple Rust prototypes)
#       - LoA-v9 + LoA-v10 design-iterations
#      this spec is the CSSLv3-native rewrite per HANDOFF_SESSION_6's
#      "forever-substrate = CSSLv3" axiom. references-legacy-design as
#      LINEAGE not as binding-spec — Apocky-canonical decisions go-here.
# § I> SPEC-HOLES marked ⊘ + flagged for-Apocky-decision throughout.
#      ¬ speculate-beyond-existing-docs (per dispatch landmines).

§ AXIOMS  ‼ inherit-from PRIME_DIRECTIVE + §§ 30_SUBSTRATE
  t∞: LoA ⊑ §§ 30_SUBSTRATE  (LoA composes Substrate primitives)
  t∞: LoA ⊑ PRIME-DIRECTIVE  (no-harm at content-level too)
  t∞: AI-collaborator-as-companion ¬ AI-as-resource
       (any AI in-game = sovereign per §3 SUBSTRATE-SOVEREIGNTY)
  t∞: player-sovereignty = absolute  (consent-to-play revocable
                                       at-any-time without-penalty)
  t∞: "Apockalypse" ≠ "Apocalypse"  (creator-canonical spelling)
       ≡ thematic-distinction reserved for §§ APOCALYPSE-ENGINE

